---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
import ProjectList from '../components/ProjectList.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
import ActionabilityList from '../components/ActionabilityList.astro';

const Projects = await getCollection('projects');
---

<Layout title="Discover | ">
	<Header
		href="ibex"
		title="Rewilding Our Ecosystems"
		body="The world's ecosystem is a complex and interconnected web of life that spans the planet, encompassing diverse environments from lush rainforests to vast deserts, and from icy polar regions to teeming coral reefs. This intricate tapestry of life, shaped over millions of years, sustains and regulates the conditions necessary for the existence of countless species, including humans. "
	/>

	<section class="mission" id="mission">
		<div class="content flex-container">
			<h2 class="title">Our Mission and Philosphy</h2><div
				class="flex-container"
			>
				<p>
					In our relentless pursuit of mitigating the greenhouse effect crisis,
					our mission revolves around immediate intervention and fostering
					long-term resilience. We actively champion renewable energy solutions,
					advocating for their widespread adoption to curb the emission of
					greenhouse gases. Collaborating with industries, policymakers, and
					communities, we aim to drive the transition to cleaner energy sources,
					thus reducing the carbon footprint and mitigating the impact of global
					warming. Simultaneously, we emphasize sustainable land use practices,
					working towards the preservation and restoration of critical
					ecosystems. Reforestation initiatives take center stage in our
					efforts, recognizing the pivotal role that trees play in sequestering
					carbon dioxide. Through engagement with scientific communities, we
					support cutting-edge research into innovative technologies that
					promise to revolutionize the way we address climate change. Our
					multifaceted approach is geared not only towards crisis management but
					also towards laying the foundations for a resilient and sustainable
					future where the threat of the greenhouse effect is effectively
					minimized.
					<br /><br />
					 Our mission does not stop at intervention alone; education and
					awareness are integral components of our strategy to combat the
					greenhouse effect crisis. We understand that a well-informed populace
					is crucial for fostering meaningful and lasting change. Through
					dynamic educational programs, we aim to demystify the complexities of
					climate change, breaking down scientific concepts into accessible and
					relatable information. Digital platforms serve as key conduits for
					reaching a global audience, allowing us to engage in interactive
					discussions, share impactful stories, and provide practical tips for
					sustainable living. Beyond this, we actively collaborate with
					educational institutions to integrate environmental education into
					formal curricula, ensuring that the next generation is equipped with
					the knowledge and skills needed for responsible stewardship of the
					planet. Our social media campaigns, community workshops, and
					partnerships with influencers further amplify our reach, creating a
					united front of environmentally conscious individuals who are not only
					aware but empowered to be agents of change in their communities and
					beyond.
				</p>
				<p>
					At the heart of our mission lies the firm belief that education and
					awareness are catalysts for transformative change. Through dynamic and
					targeted educational programs, we strive to empower individuals with a
					deep understanding of the complexities of climate change and its
					far-reaching consequences. Our initiatives extend across various
					platforms, leveraging the power of digital media to disseminate
					accessible information, engaging narratives, and real-world examples.
					By fostering a global community that is well-informed and equipped to
					navigate the intricacies of environmental challenges, we aim to create
					a groundswell of support for sustainable practices and policies.
					<br /><br />
					 In tandem with education, we actively cultivate awareness by
					integrating environmental consciousness into the fabric of society.
					Social media campaigns, community workshops, and partnerships with
					influencers serve as conduits for disseminating impactful stories and
					actionable steps towards sustainable living. We recognize that change
					is most effective when it is embraced collectively, and our mission is
					to instill a sense of responsibility in individuals and communities
					alike. By creating a movement that transcends geographical boundaries
					and cultural differences, we aspire to build a global network of
					environmentally conscious citizens committed to preserving the planet
					for current and future generations. Our overarching goal is not only
					to raise awareness but also to inspire tangible changes in behavior
					and policy, creating a ripple effect that contributes to a resilient
					and sustainable future.
				</p>
			</div>
			<figure></figure>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sustainability">
		<h2 class="title">Sustainability</h2>
		<div class="wrapper">
			<p>
				African ecosystems are incredibly diverse, encompassing rainforests,
				savannas, deserts, wetlands, and coastal areas. The continent's
				ecosystems support a vast array of flora and fauna, from the
				biodiversity of the Congo Basin rainforests to the iconic wildlife of
				the savannas, including lions, elephants, and wildebeest. The deserts of
				North and southern Africa host unique species adapted to arid
				conditions, while wetlands and coastal ecosystems are also vital parts
				of the continent's natural environment. African ecosystems provide
				essential services such as water and air purification, climate
				regulation, and soil formation, and they hold significant cultural and
				economic importance for local communities.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="projects" id="projects">
			<h6 class="subtitle">bioresponsible projects</h6>

			<ProjectList projects={Projects} />
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="restoration" id="restoration">
		<h2 class="title">Restoration</h2>
		<div class="wrapper">
			<!-- <img src="./sustainability.jpg" alt="" /> -->
			<p>
				African ecosystems are incredibly diverse, encompassing rainforests,
				savannas, deserts, wetlands, and coastal areas. The continent's
				ecosystems support a vast array of flora and fauna, from the
				biodiversity of the Congo Basin rainforests to the iconic wildlife of
				the savannas, including lions, elephants, and wildebeest. The deserts of
				North and southern Africa host unique species adapted to arid
				conditions, while wetlands and coastal ecosystems are also vital parts
				of the continent's natural environment. African ecosystems provide
				essential services such as water and air purification, climate
				regulation, and soil formation, and they hold significant cultural and
				economic importance for local communities.
			</p>
		</div>

		<article class="restore">
			<figure>
				<img
					src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517517938232-02d30ecf9f45?w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8MjJ8fGV1cm9wZWFuJTIwYmlzb258ZW58MHx8MHx8fDA%3D"
					alt="European Bison"
				/>
			</figure>
			<div class="content">
				<h3>European Bison</h3>
				<p>
					Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Facilis
					ipsam quo iure dolore omnis ut ea a, minima, architecto voluptates,
					sunt sed. Neque iste, totam molestias laboriosam corrupti quidem
					dolor.
				</p>
				<Button bg="#96B79A" text="#000" url="/restoration/european-bison">
					Read Further
				</Button>
			</div>
		</article>

		<div class="container">
			<Button bg="#96B79A" text="#000" url="/restoring">
				Read About More Restoration Projects
			</Button>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="actionability" id="actionability">
		<h2 class="title">Actionability</h2>
		<ActionabilityList />
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	section {
		position: relative;
		padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--space-s);

		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
	}

	section * {
		max-width: 60rem;
	}

	/* Mission */

	.mission {
		max-height: fit-content;
		background: #b3e3c8;
		text-align: center;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		flex-direction: column;
		place-items: center;
	}

	.mission .content {
		gap: var(--space-m);
		max-width: 80ch;
		justify-content: space-between;
	}
	.mission .flex-container {
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	.mission figure {
		background: #000;
		background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581081874314-cf94ae666228?w=600&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8Mzh8fHN1c3RhaW5hYmxlfGVufDB8fDB8fHww');
		background-position: center;
		background-repeat: no-repeat;

		min-height: 60vh;
	}

	/* Sustanability */
	.sustainability {
	}
	.sustainability .wrapper {
		position: relative;
		padding: calc(2 * var(--space-3xl)) calc(2 * var(--space-3xl)) 0rem 0rem;
		width: 100%;
		overflow: hidden;
		background: url('./sustainability.jpg');
		background-size: cover;

		@media (max-width: 600px) {
			padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-xl) 0 0;
		}
	}

	.sustainability .wrapper p {
		background: #fff;
		padding: 2rem;
		max-width: max(80%, 80ch);
		height: max-content;
	}

	/* .restoration */
	.restoration {
		background: #e9ffea;
	}

	.restoration .title {
		text-align: center;
	}
	.restoration > * {
		width: 100%;
	}
	.restoration .wrapper {
		/* width:100%; */
		height: 100%;
		position: relative;
		padding: calc(2 * var(--space-3xl)) 0 0 calc(2 * var(--space-3xl));
		width: 100%;
		overflow: hidden;
		background: url('./sustainability.jpg');
		background-size: cover;

		@media (max-width: 600px) {
			padding: var(--space-xl) 0 0 var(--space-xl);
		}
	}

	.restoration .wrapper p {
		background: #e9ffea;
		padding: 2rem;
		margin-left: auto;
		max-width: max(80%, 80ch);
		height: max-content;
	}

	.restoration article {
		display: flex;
		margin: var(--space-m) 0;
		gap: var(--space-xs);
	}
	.restoration article figure {
		height: 100vh%;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.restoration article img {
		height: 100%;
		width: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	.restoration .container {
		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
	}
</style>
